br>\r<br>在阳光下她左耳的十字架，耀眼。&nbsp;\r<br>转头，&nbsp;\r<br>『安零，你好慢啊』&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>『来了』&nbsp;\r<br>笑着跟上她。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>逃课之后。&nbsp;\r<br>她笑着对老师解释。&nbsp;\r<br>待到老师同意。&nbsp;\r<br>然后将身边的蓝发女孩儿拉出办公室。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她和她。&nbsp;\r<br>都是漂亮的女孩儿。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她，拥有许多的追随者。&nbsp;\r<br>而她，却没有一个喜欢她的人。&nbsp;\r<br>她不介意。&nbsp;\r<br>因为只要在她身边就好。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>她与她同龄。&nbsp;\r<br>她扮演的是姐姐。&nbsp;\r<br>而她却扮演的是她的妹妹，一个自负的妹妹。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>大家说她们根本不应该走在一起。&nbsp;\r<br>她沾污了她的美丽与纯洁。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她总是笑着拉过她。&nbsp;\r<br>告诉她，不要理那些讨厌的人。&nbsp;\r<br>而她，是很听话的点点头。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>星期天的下午，&nbsp;\r<br>天很蓝，云很白。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她盘腿坐在她的身边。&nbsp;\r<br>嚼着薯片，看她画画。&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她经常画的是&nbsp;\r<br>大海，蓝天，白云，小屋。&nbsp;\r<br>她奇怪的问为什么&nbsp;\r<br>她说，因为那里是最纯洁的地方&nbsp;\r<br>她似懂非懂地点头&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>她揉过她的头&nbsp;\r<br>笑，不语……&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>……只是这样…………&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她们还都是孩子…………&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>THE&nbsp;END\u0018","author":"崆陇魔女","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.320d8b06.N6nkOhY_--DwPtIJieQlxQ&fr=pb","date":"2007-05-18 20:30","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【原创·无CP】《孩子》","content":"sf","author":"崆陇魔女","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.320d8b06.N6nkOhY_--DwPtIJieQlxQ&fr=pb","date":"2007-05-18 20:30","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【原创·无CP】《孩子》","content":"d","author":"黎落澜","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.12d3a0f1.GSda4z4Bjm0aZ-RwCWqLYQ&fr=pb","date":"2007-05-18 23:20","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【原创·无CP】《孩子》","content":"D","author":"雪￡魅儿","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ec7c4b5f.KSJNpCIUJLOmFrJ1VJmBpQ&fr=pb","date":"2007-05-18 23:36","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【原创·无CP】《孩子》","content":"up","author":"崆陇魔女","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.320d8b06.N6nkOhY_--DwPtIJieQlxQ&fr=pb","date